1
00:00:06,016 --> 00:00:10,016
(2000, Three days
before Nie Feng went abroad)

2
00:00:19,796 --> 00:00:20,476
Feng,

3
00:00:20,916 --> 00:00:22,755
you're going on vacation,

4
00:00:23,236 --> 00:00:25,036
but this is too sudden!

5
00:00:25,716 --> 00:00:26,475
Come on.

6
00:00:27,196 --> 00:00:28,435
Tell me the truth.

7
00:00:31,836 --> 00:00:33,836
Are you hiding something from me?

8
00:00:40,836 --> 00:00:43,008
Look at Lu. Hasn't come back.
He's gone to ground.

9
00:00:53,952 --> 00:00:54,912
Come on, Jiasheng.

10
00:01:04,436 --> 00:01:05,236
Jiasheng,

11
00:01:06,635 --> 00:01:08,156
how is it going

12
00:01:08,672 --> 00:01:09,595
with Her Highness?

13
00:01:15,355 --> 00:01:16,155
Feng,

14
00:01:17,435 --> 00:01:18,515
I want to help.

15
00:01:19,635 --> 00:01:20,515
Publicly speaking,

16
00:01:20,956 --> 00:01:22,556
your father is a state governor.

17
00:01:22,995 --> 00:01:23,956
Privately speaking,

18
00:01:24,235 --> 00:01:26,235
he's like a father to me.

19
00:01:26,916 --> 00:01:28,316
But regarding Her Highness,

20
00:01:28,756 --> 00:01:31,036
there really isn't a good solution.

21
00:01:40,116 --> 00:01:40,795
How about this?

22
00:01:42,155 --> 00:01:43,635
I'll give you Deep In The Bustle.

23
00:01:45,396 --> 00:01:46,556
If you need it,

24
00:01:46,916 --> 00:01:48,596
I can make Lu withdraw.

25
00:01:48,916 --> 00:01:49,916
His share will go to you.

26
00:01:50,316 --> 00:01:51,116
Everything is yours.

27
00:01:53,196 --> 00:01:53,995
Jiasheng,

28
00:01:55,036 --> 00:01:58,036
you should know
how I've treated you these years.

29
00:01:59,875 --> 00:02:02,036
You think I didn't know
about Qin Wei's incident?

30
00:02:03,196 --> 00:02:04,235
I knew everything.

31
00:02:04,836 --> 00:02:06,036
I just chose not to say it.

32
00:02:07,235 --> 00:02:09,795
Because I see you as my own brother.

33
00:02:10,635 --> 00:02:12,756
What's mine is yours.

34
00:02:13,635 --> 00:02:15,835
That's why I don't hold it against you.

35
00:02:17,115 --> 00:02:19,436
Feng, that's not how it is.

36
00:02:20,196 --> 00:02:22,596
If I am holding back for profit,

37
00:02:23,036 --> 00:02:24,675
may lightning strike me dead.

38
00:02:25,075 --> 00:02:26,235
I have my difficulties.

39
00:02:28,115 --> 00:02:28,916
Moreover,

40
00:02:29,300 --> 00:02:31,936
we became sworn brothers long ago,
promising to share weal and woe.

41
00:02:31,936 --> 00:02:34,276
How could I possibly not help you?

42
00:02:45,996 --> 00:02:46,795
Tu Jiasheng,

43
00:02:48,036 --> 00:02:50,276
have you forgotten your background?

44
00:02:53,436 --> 00:02:54,596
Without me,

45
00:02:55,156 --> 00:02:57,515
could you have climbed
to Her Highness's level

46
00:02:58,115 --> 00:03:00,036
and met Paria?

47
00:03:00,756 --> 00:03:01,955
Without me,

48
00:03:02,555 --> 00:03:06,235
could you have entered the upper class?

49
00:03:06,515 --> 00:03:07,355
Yes.

50
00:03:08,716 --> 00:03:10,756
When Phachai caused trouble
at Deep In The Bustle,

51
00:03:10,756 --> 00:03:12,436
you called Her Highness

52
00:03:12,436 --> 00:03:15,235
and the Royal Guard came.

53
00:03:16,156 --> 00:03:19,316
Since then, you've risen smoothly,

54
00:03:19,316 --> 00:03:22,355
gaining legendary status.

55
00:03:23,996 --> 00:03:24,835
But

56
00:03:25,795 --> 00:03:27,716
do you even know

57
00:03:28,596 --> 00:03:30,196
your own worth?

58
00:03:33,996 --> 00:03:35,036
Now

59
00:03:35,276 --> 00:03:37,395
you and Paria broke up,

60
00:03:37,395 --> 00:03:39,635
but the bond remains.

61
00:03:40,436 --> 00:03:43,036
If you truly beg Her Highness

62
00:03:43,036 --> 00:03:44,355
and it fails,

63
00:03:45,316 --> 00:03:47,515
I won't blame you at all.

64
00:03:47,916 --> 00:03:50,196
But if you don't even try,

65
00:03:51,716 --> 00:03:52,596
I'll despise you.

66
00:03:53,996 --> 00:03:56,156
That's called ingratitude.

67
00:03:58,276 --> 00:04:00,436
But today, Jiasheng,

68
00:04:01,835 --> 00:04:03,955
I'm forcing your hand.

69
00:04:07,955 --> 00:04:09,515
Make a choice today.

70
00:04:10,036 --> 00:04:11,756
Either help me one last time

71
00:04:11,756 --> 00:04:14,036
and plead with Her Highness again.

72
00:04:14,515 --> 00:04:16,476
Or use this gun

73
00:04:17,235 --> 00:04:18,716
to kill me.

74
00:04:19,635 --> 00:04:20,515
Without your help,

75
00:04:20,515 --> 00:04:21,716
I won't survive, after all.

76
00:04:24,916 --> 00:04:25,795
Choose.

77
00:04:36,672 --> 00:04:39,936
=The Glory Fades=

78
00:04:39,936 --> 00:04:42,624
=Episode 32=
(Threat)

79
00:04:42,752 --> 00:04:45,916
Did you send someone to kill An Ruoxi?

80
00:04:50,636 --> 00:04:51,435
No?

81
00:04:52,435 --> 00:04:53,276
Look.

82
00:04:53,836 --> 00:04:54,755
Take a look.

83
00:04:55,755 --> 00:04:57,152
Look at

84
00:04:57,152 --> 00:05:02,435
Mr. Tu Jiasheng, my fifth brother,
hailed as a legendary figure.

85
00:05:03,435 --> 00:05:05,355
From the moment he entered,

86
00:05:05,675 --> 00:05:09,235
he hasn't asked about me once

87
00:05:09,836 --> 00:05:12,956
like how I've been all these years,

88
00:05:13,355 --> 00:05:15,235
whether I sleep well

89
00:05:15,555 --> 00:05:17,555
or eat properly.

90
00:05:18,235 --> 00:05:19,995
All his thoughts

91
00:05:20,195 --> 00:05:22,555
are on two women.

92
00:05:23,036 --> 00:05:24,195
To be precise,

93
00:05:24,276 --> 00:05:26,875
on that pair of sisters.

94
00:05:27,755 --> 00:05:29,836
He really is a romantic!

95
00:05:34,755 --> 00:05:35,675
You

96
00:05:37,555 --> 00:05:39,115
killed her because of that?

97
00:05:41,036 --> 00:05:42,235
She didn't do anything wrong.

98
00:05:42,516 --> 00:05:43,675
Yeah.

99
00:05:43,675 --> 00:05:45,916
She really didn't do anything wrong.

100
00:05:47,156 --> 00:05:49,184
She was just trying to persuade us

101
00:05:49,184 --> 00:05:51,036
to close Deep In The Bustle

102
00:05:51,675 --> 00:05:54,636
to retire from the life of crime,

103
00:05:54,675 --> 00:05:56,736
to abandon evil for good

104
00:05:56,736 --> 00:05:59,076
and to live ordinary lives.

105
00:06:00,468 --> 00:06:01,348
I warned her

106
00:06:01,348 --> 00:06:02,747
to stop dreaming.

107
00:06:02,747 --> 00:06:05,867
Wouldn't it be better
to just be madam peacefully?

108
00:06:06,668 --> 00:06:07,908
She wouldn't listen.

109
00:06:08,947 --> 00:06:09,908
But it's right.

110
00:06:10,228 --> 00:06:12,228
If you have a dream,
you should pursue it.

111
00:06:12,947 --> 00:06:14,908
Don't you think it's ridiculous?

112
00:06:27,547 --> 00:06:28,427
So

113
00:06:29,908 --> 00:06:30,947
you killed her?

114
00:06:31,747 --> 00:06:34,427
I didn't!

115
00:06:35,627 --> 00:06:37,348
Jiasheng,

116
00:06:38,307 --> 00:06:41,468
I told you years ago

117
00:06:41,468 --> 00:06:42,947
not to keep her.

118
00:06:43,268 --> 00:06:44,867
Yet you developed real feelings for her.

119
00:06:44,867 --> 00:06:47,268
This is a major taboo
in our line of work.

120
00:06:47,268 --> 00:06:47,987
But

121
00:06:48,307 --> 00:06:50,067
you wouldn't listen.

122
00:06:51,348 --> 00:06:52,708
For An Ruoxi,

123
00:06:52,708 --> 00:06:55,148
you gave up the support of Her Highness.

124
00:06:55,668 --> 00:06:57,108
Don't you think it's a pity?

125
00:06:57,908 --> 00:06:59,268
What a shame.

126
00:07:01,268 --> 00:07:02,268
But

127
00:07:02,708 --> 00:07:04,747
I really didn't kill her.

128
00:07:05,747 --> 00:07:07,268
I have

129
00:07:07,547 --> 00:07:09,627
been wrong,

130
00:07:10,507 --> 00:07:16,067
worse than Dou E.

131
00:07:32,128 --> 00:07:33,028
Ruoxi,

132
00:07:34,268 --> 00:07:35,708
now can you tell me

133
00:07:36,708 --> 00:07:38,387
if everything I did for you

134
00:07:38,788 --> 00:07:39,987
is right

135
00:07:40,828 --> 00:07:42,108
or wrong?

136
00:07:48,708 --> 00:07:49,468
Hello, Chu Bai.

137
00:07:50,028 --> 00:07:51,148
Did you get it?

138
00:07:51,427 --> 00:07:52,187
No.

139
00:07:52,668 --> 00:07:53,788
The folder was found.

140
00:07:53,788 --> 00:07:55,908
But all the directories inside
are empty.

141
00:07:55,908 --> 00:07:57,947
They must have been deleted
or moved in advance.

142
00:08:02,307 --> 00:08:03,228
I figured as much.

143
00:08:04,108 --> 00:08:05,788
Tu Jiasheng is so cunning.

144
00:08:05,788 --> 00:08:08,228
Maybe he was prepared long ago.

145
00:08:09,428 --> 00:08:10,229
Now it seems

146
00:08:10,428 --> 00:08:11,229
the only hope

147
00:08:11,229 --> 00:08:13,068
is what Ruoxi obtained before she died.

148
00:08:13,349 --> 00:08:14,589
Still no clues?

149
00:08:15,669 --> 00:08:16,469
No.

150
00:08:17,188 --> 00:08:18,789
She never told me about it.

151
00:08:19,549 --> 00:08:20,748
Think harder.

152
00:08:21,308 --> 00:08:22,149
Besides the diary,

153
00:08:22,149 --> 00:08:23,308
what else did she give you?

154
00:08:23,828 --> 00:08:25,589
Don't miss any useful information.

155
00:08:27,428 --> 00:08:28,909
Really nothing else.

156
00:08:29,428 --> 00:08:31,229
I've thought of everything I could.

157
00:08:33,149 --> 00:08:34,469
That's strange.

158
00:08:36,828 --> 00:08:38,229
Chu Bai, I...

159
00:08:39,232 --> 00:08:39,868
Hello, Yunian?

160
00:08:39,868 --> 00:08:40,508
What happened?

161
00:08:40,508 --> 00:08:41,148
Su Yunian.

162
00:08:41,229 --> 00:08:41,989
Su Yunian.

163
00:08:43,148 --> 00:08:44,469
One week before the incident,

164
00:08:45,268 --> 00:08:46,829
she said she was going out to relax.

165
00:08:48,069 --> 00:08:49,309
She went to see you, right?

166
00:08:51,189 --> 00:08:51,989
That's right.

167
00:08:52,908 --> 00:08:54,668
So if I really wanted to kill her,

168
00:08:54,668 --> 00:08:56,908
why wouldn't I just make her disappear?

169
00:08:57,309 --> 00:08:59,008
No body, no crime.

170
00:08:59,008 --> 00:09:00,672
Wouldn't that have been cleaner?

171
00:09:03,069 --> 00:09:04,229
She went to see you.

172
00:09:04,709 --> 00:09:05,709
What did she say?

173
00:09:07,429 --> 00:09:09,709
Have you been drinking too much lately

174
00:09:09,709 --> 00:09:11,989
and ruining your brain?

175
00:09:13,028 --> 00:09:16,109
She persuaded us to retire from crime,

176
00:09:16,109 --> 00:09:17,829
and put down the butcher's knife,

177
00:09:17,829 --> 00:09:20,469
to become a Buddha on the spot.

178
00:09:20,469 --> 00:09:21,788
Nonsense!

179
00:09:23,469 --> 00:09:24,309
Feng,

180
00:09:25,069 --> 00:09:26,429
until now,

181
00:09:26,589 --> 00:09:28,388
I haven't said a negative word

182
00:09:28,388 --> 00:09:30,469
about you to anyone, including Lu.

183
00:09:31,628 --> 00:09:34,309
I bowed my head to the ground
and swore brotherhood with you.

184
00:09:34,309 --> 00:09:36,576
I've fulfilled my duty
as a younger brother.

185
00:09:36,576 --> 00:09:38,028
I've treated you as my brother.

186
00:09:38,589 --> 00:09:39,508
Feng,

187
00:09:40,429 --> 00:09:41,148
don't

188
00:09:42,109 --> 00:09:44,109
push me too far!

189
00:09:47,508 --> 00:09:48,469
Really?

190
00:09:49,189 --> 00:09:51,668
Never say a negative word?

191
00:09:51,668 --> 00:09:52,388
Yes.

192
00:09:52,829 --> 00:09:54,508
I never mentioned the Cabinet

193
00:09:54,508 --> 00:09:56,469
traced it back to your father

194
00:09:56,908 --> 00:09:59,508
or you went abroad to avoid the heat.

195
00:09:59,668 --> 00:10:00,668
And I never said

196
00:10:00,668 --> 00:10:01,309
you

197
00:10:01,589 --> 00:10:02,508
forced me

198
00:10:02,589 --> 00:10:04,908
to grovel and beg Her Highness
for mercy,

199
00:10:04,908 --> 00:10:06,429
so your father could

200
00:10:06,429 --> 00:10:07,508
sail through unscathed.

201
00:10:08,469 --> 00:10:09,268
Feng,

202
00:10:09,908 --> 00:10:12,589
I haven't told anyone about any of this,

203
00:10:12,908 --> 00:10:13,868
not even Lu.

204
00:10:19,028 --> 00:10:20,709
Oh, Jiasheng,

205
00:10:21,309 --> 00:10:22,268
well done.

206
00:10:22,908 --> 00:10:25,668
You truly are a model of loyalty.

207
00:10:27,189 --> 00:10:28,109
But, Jiasheng,

208
00:10:29,508 --> 00:10:30,949
don't you think over the years,

209
00:10:32,028 --> 00:10:33,788
you've become a bit too arrogant?

210
00:10:34,309 --> 00:10:35,309
Arrogant?

211
00:10:35,908 --> 00:10:37,109
What arrogance?

212
00:10:37,309 --> 00:10:38,429
What level of arrogance

213
00:10:38,429 --> 00:10:39,508
could make you

214
00:10:39,508 --> 00:10:41,028
want me dead so badly?

215
00:10:41,028 --> 00:10:41,829
Fine.

216
00:10:41,829 --> 00:10:43,268
Then let me tell you.

217
00:10:43,829 --> 00:10:44,788
Let me ask you.

218
00:10:45,028 --> 00:10:47,309
For that old Qin Wei deal,

219
00:10:47,709 --> 00:10:48,788
did An Ruoxi,

220
00:10:48,788 --> 00:10:50,709
that girl, meddled?

221
00:10:52,109 --> 00:10:54,069
Yet you refused to help Qin Wei,

222
00:10:54,709 --> 00:10:58,028
and sided with her against me.

223
00:10:58,268 --> 00:11:00,829
Isn't that arrogance?

224
00:11:00,829 --> 00:11:03,388
That was an unconscionable act!

225
00:11:03,388 --> 00:11:04,989
Deep In The Bustle

226
00:11:04,989 --> 00:11:06,272
simply doesn't do such things.

227
00:11:06,272 --> 00:11:08,268
That's called arrogance!

228
00:11:09,829 --> 00:11:12,508
Overweening arrogance!

229
00:11:24,069 --> 00:11:26,429
Back then, you even said

230
00:11:27,109 --> 00:11:29,268
you wanted to hand Deep In The Bustle
over to me.

231
00:11:29,628 --> 00:11:31,668
Fine. I'll give you Deep In The Bustle.

232
00:11:33,508 --> 00:11:34,949
If you need it,

233
00:11:34,949 --> 00:11:36,668
I can make Lu withdraw.

234
00:11:37,028 --> 00:11:38,189
His share will go to you.

235
00:11:38,272 --> 00:11:39,189
Everything is yours.

236
00:11:39,388 --> 00:11:41,028
And just because of this one thing,

237
00:11:41,508 --> 00:11:42,989
you accuse me of being arrogant?

238
00:11:43,229 --> 00:11:44,628
Holding a grudge?

239
00:11:46,429 --> 00:11:47,109
Bravo.

240
00:11:47,309 --> 00:11:47,989
Bravo.

241
00:11:48,229 --> 00:11:48,908
Bravo.

242
00:11:49,148 --> 00:11:50,469
Not just arrogant,

243
00:11:50,469 --> 00:11:52,589
you're also wildly ambitious,

244
00:11:52,589 --> 00:11:53,429
Tu Jiasheng.

245
00:11:54,469 --> 00:11:55,829
Jiasheng,

246
00:11:56,868 --> 00:11:58,268
when I said that,

247
00:11:58,548 --> 00:12:00,028
it was mere politeness.

248
00:12:01,109 --> 00:12:02,709
If you took it seriously,

249
00:12:03,829 --> 00:12:04,349
that's called

250
00:12:04,349 --> 00:12:06,109
not knowing your place.

251
00:12:13,309 --> 00:12:14,989
Times have changed.

252
00:12:15,668 --> 00:12:17,508
Now your father

253
00:12:18,388 --> 00:12:19,989
has safely transitioned

254
00:12:19,989 --> 00:12:21,429
into the Cabinet,

255
00:12:21,429 --> 00:12:23,028
becoming the third most powerful figure,

256
00:12:23,028 --> 00:12:25,388
on equal footing with Her Highness,

257
00:12:25,908 --> 00:12:28,589
so you forgot your desperate pleas
to me back then,

258
00:12:28,628 --> 00:12:30,668
and treat me like a mouse,

259
00:12:30,668 --> 00:12:33,429
while you act like a cat toying
with me at will,

260
00:12:33,429 --> 00:12:35,829
ready to kill me anytime.

261
00:12:35,829 --> 00:12:37,028
Right?

262
00:12:37,268 --> 00:12:38,829
So what if I am?

263
00:12:41,709 --> 00:12:42,668
Tu Jiasheng,

264
00:12:43,989 --> 00:12:44,768
do you think that,

265
00:12:44,768 --> 00:12:47,709
as you hold dirt on those officials now,

266
00:12:47,709 --> 00:12:49,109
you can

267
00:12:49,589 --> 00:12:52,508
run rampant through Changqingtai City,

268
00:12:52,508 --> 00:12:54,069
do whatever you please,

269
00:12:55,069 --> 00:12:58,189
and make He Mike lose Cong in middle age

270
00:12:58,628 --> 00:13:00,668
and Lin Fuyi's lineage end?

271
00:13:02,109 --> 00:13:03,109
Do you still think

272
00:13:03,109 --> 00:13:04,148
you're still

273
00:13:04,148 --> 00:13:06,829
Her Highness's prospective son-in-law,

274
00:13:06,989 --> 00:13:08,709
so when trouble finds you,

275
00:13:08,709 --> 00:13:11,908
she'll step out to help you?

276
00:13:13,229 --> 00:13:14,429
Tu Jiasheng,

277
00:13:15,388 --> 00:13:19,349
you've made your bed, now lie in it!

278
00:13:40,268 --> 00:13:41,189
Tu Jiasheng,

279
00:13:41,908 --> 00:13:43,268
is it you?

280
00:13:44,028 --> 00:13:45,189
Tu Jiasheng,

281
00:13:46,709 --> 00:13:48,429
you liar!

282
00:13:48,908 --> 00:13:50,709
Did you kill An Ruoxi?

283
00:13:52,788 --> 00:13:53,908
Tu Jiasheng,

284
00:13:54,709 --> 00:13:55,949
come out!

285
00:13:56,309 --> 00:13:58,069
Do you dare show yourself?

286
00:14:11,268 --> 00:14:12,508
It's you.

287
00:14:12,989 --> 00:14:13,868
No mistake.

288
00:14:14,109 --> 00:14:14,788
It's me.

289
00:14:15,069 --> 00:14:16,868
You killed An Ruoxi?

290
00:14:26,420 --> 00:14:30,094
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

291
00:14:30,393 --> 00:14:33,584
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

292
00:14:35,416 --> 00:14:39,037
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

293
00:14:39,586 --> 00:14:42,385
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

294
00:14:43,856 --> 00:14:47,586
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

295
00:14:47,810 --> 00:14:51,307
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

296
00:14:52,706 --> 00:14:56,393
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

297
00:14:57,031 --> 00:15:02,146
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

298
00:15:02,850 --> 00:15:06,984
♪I feel guilty♪

299
00:15:07,554 --> 00:15:11,298
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

300
00:15:12,162 --> 00:15:15,605
♪Even in tears♪

301
00:15:16,354 --> 00:15:20,268
♪It doesn't matter♪

302
00:15:20,450 --> 00:15:24,273
♪We embrace in dreams♪

303
00:15:25,122 --> 00:15:28,560
♪I let down all my defenses♪

304
00:15:29,794 --> 00:15:33,157
♪Though the story has its end♪

305
00:15:33,922 --> 00:15:42,274
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
